messages.message:
:female-teacher: Patch Professor Announcement: *Patch TA is now running on our dogfood-deploy pipeline!*

Any merged pull request with the `patch-professor/staged-dogfood` label will have the attached dogfood patches automatically applied during dogfood deployments. This label is automatically added on Patch Professor runs and automatically removed when applied. You shouldn’t need to manually add any labels for Patch Professor to work anymore. The Patch Professor docs (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/TI/pages/1847918652/Patch+Professor) has been updated to reflect this new process.

Please reach out to me if you have any questions or encounter any problems. I’m always happy to help!
